**S-014 — Fix BIDIR direction resolution to use local IO pressure**
*Fixes A2*
Rewrite TASK-058 to use local IO pressure instead of T2 aggregate pressure:
```typescript
function resolveBidirDirection(ioNode: T1Node, neighborIoNode: T1Node): 'send'|'receive'|'idle' {
  const localP = totalEnergy(ioNode.energy) / ioNode.capacity;
  const neighborP = totalEnergy(neighborIoNode.energy) / neighborIoNode.capacity;
  const delta = localP - neighborP;
  if (Math.abs(delta) < 0.05) return 'idle';
  return delta > 0 ? 'send' : 'receive';
}
```
This uses the same pressure signal as passive flow computation (TASK-053), eliminating the conflict.

**S-015 — Total outgoing flow cap per T1 node**
*Fixes A3*
